NagiosPlugins
=============

This module provides an API to easily build a nagios plugins.

The main idee is that a nagios plugins devel only focus on retrieving data and let API do the rest.

Features :
   - Create and manage options nagios plugins
   - Build counters
   - Parse and check thresholds

EXAMPLE

A simple memory check script can be found in "examples/check_memory.pl"
